type: web_research
title: Dual Investment自動化システム - OSS Trading Bot & システム設計パターン調査
key_insights[10]: "Freqtrade: Python 3.11+, IStrategy基底クラス, populate_indicators/entry/exit_trend, FreqAI (ML統合), CCXT経由Bitget対応","Passivbot v7.8: Python+Rust, Martingale DCA Grid, WebSocket pure maker, wallet_exposure_limit, Bitgetネイティブ対応","OpenTrader: TypeScript monorepo, pnpm workspace, GRID/DCA/RSI戦略, Fastify RPC + React UI, CCXT 100+取引所","Hummingbot: 5層アーキテクチャ, V2 Controller-Executor pattern, Clock tick system, 23+コネクタ, Gateway DEX対応","FreqAI: IFreqaiModel + FreqaiDataKitchen + FreqaiDataDrawer, LightGBM/XGBoost/PyTorch/RL, スライディングウィンドウバックテスト","CCXT MCP Server: npm @lazydino/ccxt-mcp, 100+取引所, REST API主体(WebSocket制限あり)","時系列DB: ClickHouse(大規模分析最速) > TimescaleDB(SQL互換) > InfluxDB(リアルタイム+圧縮効率)","メッセージキュー: Redis Streams(軽量低遅延) vs Kafka(大規模永続化) - 小規模ならRedis推奨","Dual Investment: Buy Low/Sell High structured product, strike price + settlement date, 自動決済","データパイプライン: Dagster(アセット中心) vs Prefect(クラウドネイティブ) vs Airflow(大規模DAG)"
findings[7]: "Freqtrade IStrategy: timeframe, stoploss, minimal_roi, custom callbacks, DataProvider API","Passivbot: passivbot-rust for order computation, Forager feature for dynamic market selection","Hummingbot V2: PositionExecutor, GridExecutor, TWAPExecutor, MarketMakingController, DirectionalTradingController","Freqtrade Telegram RPC: RPCManager → RPCHandler chain, @authorized_only decorator, 30+ commands","CCXT rate limiter: leaky bucket (default) or rolling window, exponential backoff on 429","WebSocket reconnection: exponential backoff 1s→60s, 5 retry attempts, hybrid REST+WS architecture","Security: HashiCorp Vault dynamic secrets with TTL, IP restriction on exchange API, never hardcode keys"
refs[6]: "Freqtrade: github.com/freqtrade/freqtrade - IStrategy, FreqAI, RPC/Telegram","Passivbot: github.com/enarjord/passivbot - src/, passivbot-rust/, configs/","OpenTrader: github.com/Open-Trader/opentrader - packages/bot-templates, exchanges, indicators","Hummingbot: github.com/hummingbot/hummingbot - V2 framework, ConnectorBase, MarketsRecorder","CCXT MCP: github.com/lazy-dinosaur/ccxt-mcp - TypeScript MCP server","FreqAI DeepWiki: deepwiki.com/freqtrade/freqtrade/5.1-freqai-machine-learning"
recommendations[6]: Dual Investment自動化にはCCXT + カスタムMCPサーバーの組み合わせが最適,バックテストエンジンはFreqtradeのスライディングウィンドウ方式を参考に実装,リアルタイムデータ処理はRedis Streams + WebSocket hybrid構成,時系列データ保存はClickHouse (分析) + Redis (リアルタイムキャッシュ) の二層構成,Telegram通知はFreqtradeのRPC/Telegram設計パターンを流用,セキュリティはHashiCorp Vault + 取引所API IP制限 + 環境変数の三層防御
